NOTE: one real field-loss bug surfaced+fixed during this proof — items that are BOTH
blocked AND gated (e.g. ready-f94) dropped their gate on the nostr projection because
applyDepAndGateStatus cleared waiting_type/waiting_on/gate_msg_id whenever status!=waiting.
pkg/state.applyBlockStatus keeps those fields under blocking; the projection now mirrors it.
